text: Premiera is a 1976 Romanian comedy movie. Mihai Constantinescu directed it. Tamara Buciuceanu, Carmen Stănescu, Radu Beligan, Toma Caragiu, Dem Rădulescu, Vasilica Tastaman, Aurel Giurumia, Carmen Galin, and Gheorghe Dinică acted in it. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 comedy movies Category:Romanian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Mihai Constantinescu
title: Premiera
